+ * - C=float32:
+ *   - A=float16, B=float16: K % 16 == 0
+ *   - A=bfloat16, B=bfloat16: K % 16 == 0
+ *   - A=float32, B=float32: require (!trans_A && trans_B) and K % 8 == 0
+ *   - Various float8 mixes: require (!trans_A && trans_B) and K % 32 == 0
+ * - C=int32:
